00:00:32.540 --> 00:00:37.150
However, his luck changes when he meets his
beautiful next-door neighbour Danielle.

00:00:37.150 --> 00:00:40.910
The outlandish Danielle and the steady Matthew
each turn out to be the perfect complement

00:00:40.910 --> 00:00:43.890
for the other, and they are immediately smitten
with one another.

00:00:43.890 --> 00:00:48.350
However, the relationship is challenged when
Matthew discovers through his porn-enthusiast

00:00:48.350 --> 00:00:54.350
friend Eli that Danielle was recently an adult
film actress under the stage name "Athena".

00:00:54.350 --> 00:00:58.110
Following Eli's advice on how to deal with
this incredible revelation, Matthew takes

00:00:58.110 --> 00:01:00.480
Danielle to a sleazy motel.

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:03.989
Danielle guesses that Matthew has discovered
her past and punishes him by performing a

00:01:03.989 --> 00:01:07.229
