ends the relationship.

00:01:15.640 --> 00:01:19.490
Matthew goes to Danielle's house the following
day and attempts to reconcile with her, but

00:01:19.490 --> 00:01:24.670
learns that she is returning to the porn industry,
and is leaving for Las Vegas with her ex-boyfriend,

00:01:24.670 --> 00:01:26.210
porn producer Kelly.

00:01:26.210 --> 00:01:31.490
Matthew, riddled with guilt and remorse, follows
Danielle to Las Vegas to find her performing

00:01:31.490 --> 00:01:37.219
