00:01:47.649 --> 00:01:52.119
Kelly offers to let him erase his debt by
breaking into rival producer Hugo Posh's home

00:01:52.119 --> 00:01:56.590
to steal an award statuette, but after Matthew
has entered the house Kelly calls in a robbery

00:01:56.590 --> 00:01:59.049
