00:01:59.049 --> 00:02:02.919
Matthew narrowly avoids the police and rushes
to his scholarship award dinner.

00:02:02.919 --> 00:02:07.340
High on ecstasy that Kelly told him was aspirin,
he improvises a deeply sentimental speech

00:02:07.340 --> 00:02:11.950
